RISK
Unforeseen events (such as a team member falling ill/ dropping out) could jeopardize our project plan.


Do you have any advice on how and where to build buffers into our project plan?


We do not want to rely too heavily on a particular team member.
What are some examples of how previous groups accomplished this?


How did other groups reduce the importance of original authors so that other group members could fill in as required?
